in a blender, but ain't life a bitch.

189
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:12,089
No, you're not understanding me!
I want you to confess!

190
00:10:12,410 --> 00:10:14,370
- Confess?
- Confess!

191
00:10:15,209 --> 00:10:19,290
