648
00:33:52,050 --> 00:33:54,210
"I'm gonna charge my phone
in an interrogation room."

649
00:33:55,490 --> 00:33:56,490
Who does that?

650
00:33:57,649 --> 00:33:58,849
Don't forget your phone!

651
00:34:02,329 --> 00:34:03,369
I'm gonna piss!

652
00:34:04,609 --> 00:34:06,250
"The Confesstigators."

