00:34:06,730 --> 00:34:08,410
Hey, it ain't ruining my life.

654
00:34:11,490 --> 00:34:15,289
Thanks so much for watching.
We're off next week. Good night!

655
00:34:18,169 --> 00:34:19,169
G...

